headline.print_headline: Cain Is Perfect for 5 Innings but Cubs Top Giants
headline.main: Cain Is Perfect for 5 Innings but Cubs Top Giants

lead_paragraph: Matt Cain pitched five perfect innings for the San Francisco Giants on Monday, but the Chicago Cubs rallied for a 3-2 victory.
